== 帝国时代III：决定版 ==
重制版《[[世紀帝國III：決定版|世紀帝國III：決定版]]》于2020年10月16日上市。决定版对原作游戏的画质和音乐进行了重制，并新增了印加和瑞典两个文明。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://new.qq.com/omn/20201017/20201017A06AMQ00.html |title=《帝国时代3：决定版》回炉重制反而评价下降，优化还需加强 |access-date=2020-10-23 |archive-date=2020-10-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201027044436/https://new.qq.com/omn/20201017/20201017A06AMQ00.html }}</ref>

2019年5月30日，微軟宣佈所有的世紀帝國決定版，將在steam上販售，並聲明更多的資訊將在近期內發佈。世紀帝國III：決定版是由{{le|Tantalus Media|Tantalus Media}}所開發，並由[[Xbox游戏工作室|Xbox游戏工作室]]內部的World's Edge工作室所監督。<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.pcgamesinsider.biz/news/69560/gamescom-2019-microsofts-new-age-of-empires-arm-isnt-a-developer-firm-overseeing-other-studios-working-on-ip/ | title = Gamescom 2019 - Microsoft's new Age of Empires arm isn't a developer, firm overseeing other studios working on IP | first = Alex | last = Calvin | date = August 20, 2019 | accessdate = August 20, 2019 | work = [[PGGamesInsider.biz|PGGamesInsider.biz]] | archive-date = 2019-08-20 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190820152511/https://www.pcgamesinsider.biz/news/69560/gamescom-2019-microsofts-new-age-of-empires-arm-isnt-a-developer-firm-overseeing-other-studios-working-on-ip/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>

